RACE.FOOTNOTES: DIM THE LIGHTS took the early lead then set a comfortable cushion between rival the entire race. KING BRYCE was at least four wide most of the race then coming down the stretch ran against CASH CRUZER then got the nod at the wire. CASH CRUZER ran evenly throughout the race then dueled KING BRYCE down the last half furlong and got outnodded at the wire. SLEEPY EYES ran off pace from the leader then coming down to the last sixteenth faded slightly as foes pulled away. ETHAN broke a little slow but caught up quick to maintain the pace in the middle of the pack then coming down the stretch had a late kick. MILD DISTRACTION ran in evenly in the middle of the pack on the rail. SEA OF INDY ran in the middle of the pack three wide then shuffled back going into the turn. ARBITRO ran at the back of the pack then coming on the stretch had a late kick to make up some ground. DON HOLLYWOOD ran two wide for most of the race then coming on to the stretch faded back. JR'S CONFIDENCE ran at the back of the pack then coming into the turn slowed to last place. THIS RACE WAS HAND TIMED.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: HEAR ME ROAR ran off pace in the three path then in the middle of the stretch really had a strong close to win the race. DOUBLE STORM had good early speed then maintained the pace with HEAR ME ROAR down the stretch but just couldn't match the closing pace. LAS TRES MARIPOSAS set the early pace continued with a great pace but the pressure from DOUBLE STORM and HEAR ME ROAR got to them and tired out late stretch. SEE YOU AT THE TOP ran evenly throughout the entire race. ARTFUL ROSE was off slow from the break but still made a good gain coming on to the stretch. PREMEDITATED LILY started to gain ground on the leaders but the pace was too quick and ended up tiring late into the stretch. CAROLYN'S WAY ran with an even pace throughout the race did not kick on the stretch. JEDI JENNIE showed little interest in racing but ran even throughout the race. MAMACITA CARTIER started in the middle of the pack then slowly slowed throughout the race. MISS TRICKY INDY trailed throughout the race. THIS RACE WAS HAND TIMED.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: MINE THAT STAR ran off pace then around the turn went to the the rail to close the distance on the leaders came out of the turn in the middle of the track and continued to drive hard moved to the inside to avoid foes and over took rivals within the last fifty yards. HOORAY AUSTIN dueled LEAVE THEM BEHIND for most of the race then about midway thru the stretch pulled away and started dueling TRUTH SEEKER for the last half furlong. TRUTH SEEKER ran in the middle of the pack then coming out of the turn on the outside made a strong rally and caught up to the leaders and dueled for second place. TULANE TRYST ran on the rail to close the distance then drifted out to open lane and closed with strong effort. MASTERING ran at the front of the middle pack then coming down the stretch faded back. MINISTER OF SOUL ran in the middle of the pack then shuffled back as the race went on. LEAVE THEM BEHIND had good early speed dueled with HOORAY AUSTIN then in the middle of the stretch got tired out and lost ground to the back. CYBERVIKING trailed throughout the race.
